PREAMBLE

This E-Commerce Storefront Software is released under a DUAL-LICENSE model:
  • FREE TIER for non-commercial and educational use
  • PAID TIER for commercial use with royalty obligations

The license you are eligible for depends on your use case, not your intent.
If you profit from this Software in any way, a Commercial License is required.

