SECTION 1: GRANT OF LICENSE (DUAL-LICENSE MODEL)

The Licensor (Himanshu) utilizes a Dual-License model to ensure this Software
remains freely accessible for education and open innovation, while requiring
fair compensation for commercial exploitation.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1.1 NON-COMMERCIAL & EDUCATIONAL USE (FREE TIER)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Subject to full compliance with the Attribution Conditions detailed below,
the Licensor hereby grants you a worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive
license to use, copy, modify, and distribute this Software strictly for:

  ✅ PERSONAL LEARNING
     Self-education, portfolio building, skill development, and local tinkering

  ✅ ACADEMIC & EDUCATIONAL
     University projects, coursework, hackathons, capstones, and internships

  ✅ OPEN-SOURCE CONTRIBUTIONS
     Contributing improvements to this project or compatible open-source projects

  ✅ NON-PROFIT ORGANIZATIONS
     Registered charities, NGOs, or educational organizations where NO revenue
     is generated from the platform itself

CONDITIONS OF FREE TIER USE:
  • You must retain all copyright headers and attribution
  • You must not remove or hide the attribution in your deployment
  • You must not use this for ANY revenue-generating activity
  • If you monetize, you MUST immediately obtain a Commercial License

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1.2 COMMERCIAL USE RESTRICTION (PAID TIER REQUIRED)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

You may NOT use this Software for Commercial Purposes under the Free Tier.
You MUST obtain and maintain a valid Commercial License.

"COMMERCIAL PURPOSES" is strictly defined as ANY use case designed to generate
direct or indirect profit, including but not limited to:

  ❌ Deploying a live, revenue-generating e-commerce storefront
  ❌ Use by any registered corporate entity, partnership, or business
  ❌ Use by freelancers, agencies building for paying clients
  ❌ Offering as SaaS/hosted service
  ❌ Any monetization whatsoever

CLEAR RULE: If you or your organization make ANY money (directly or indirectly)
using this Software, a Commercial License is required.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1.3 OBTAINING A COMMERCIAL LICENSE
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If you intend to use this Software for Commercial Purposes, you MUST obtain
a separate Commercial Software License prior to first deployment.

COMMERCIAL LICENSE INCLUDES:
  ✓ Rights to deploy in production for revenue-generating purposes
  ✓ 5-10% monthly royalty model (tiered by annual revenue)
  ✓ Detailed terms at: COMMERCIAL-LICENSE.md
  ✓ Formal License Agreement (COMMERCIAL-LICENSE-AGREEMENT.md)
  ✓ Monthly reporting (by 15th of each month)
  ✓ Optional: dedicated support (negotiable)

TO OBTAIN A COMMERCIAL LICENSE:
  Email: hk8913114@gmail.com
  Subject: "Commercial License - [Your Company Name]"
  Include: Company name, nature of business, expected monthly revenue

PRICING:
  • 5% monthly royalty for annual revenue ₹0-₹50 Lakhs
  • 10% monthly royalty for annual revenue ₹50 Lakhs and above
  • Payment due by 15th of each month
  • No upfront fees, no setup costs
  • Minimum 12-month term

