SECTION 3: ENFORCEMENT & VIOLATIONS

Commercial use WITHOUT a valid Commercial License:
  ❌ Using for revenue-generating purposes
  ❌ Deployed by registered business entity
  ❌ Accepting any payment from customers/clients
  ❌ Any monetization whatsoever

Violations constitute willful copyright infringement under Indian Copyright
Act, 1957. The Licensor reserves the right to pursue:

  💰 FINANCIAL DAMAGES:
     • ₹30,000-₹1,00,000 per day of violation
     • ₹75,000+ per removed header
     • ₹1,00,000-₹2,50,000 per hidden attribution
     • Retroactive royalties at 15% penalty rate

  ⚖️ LEGAL REMEDIES:
     • DMCA takedown notices
     • Injunctive relief
     • Legal action & damages

CURE PERIODS:
  • First violation: 7 days
  • Second violation: 3 days
  • Third+ violation: Immediate termination

